StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetTotalCountUncer..edOso369EvalTask]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@TrainingFileID uniqueidentifier
AS
BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT Count(*) as TotalCount FROM USMC.Evalua.onTask et, USMC.Mul.MonthEvalua.on me
WHERE et.Mul.MonthEvalua.onId=me.ID AND me.TrainingFileID=@TrainingFileID AND (EvalSignatureID IS NULL OR OSOSignatureID IS NULL)
END
